                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for optimizing reduction behavior of hydrogen-based shaft furnace burden through ore-coke mixed loading and application of method",
                    "通过矿焦混装优化氢基竖炉炉料还原行为的方法及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of low-carbon metallurgy, in particular to a method for optimizing the reduction behavior of a hydrogen-based shaft furnace charge through ore-coke mixed loading and application thereof.The method for optimizing the reduction behavior of the hydrogen-based shaft furnace charge through ore-coke mixed loading comprises the following steps that a, oxidized pellets and lump ore are evenly mixed according to the proportion, and an ore sample is obtained; b, mixing coke with a preset mass percent into the ore sample; and c, mixing the coke and the ore sample, and putting the mixture into a furnace for smelting. According to the invention, the furnace charge reduction time under the same reduction degree can be effectively shortened, the furnace charge bonding is reduced, the reduction gas demand is reduced, and the reduction cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及低碳冶金技术领域，具体涉及一种通过矿焦混装优化氢基竖炉炉料还原行为的方法及其应用，其中，通过矿焦混装优化氢基竖炉炉料还原行为的方法包括以下步骤：a.将氧化球团及块矿按比例进行混匀，得到矿样；b.向矿样中混入预定质量百分比的焦炭；c.将焦炭和矿样混合后装入炉内进行冶炼。通过本发明，能够有效缩短相同还原度下炉料还原时间，减轻炉料粘结，降低还原气需求量，减少还原成本。"
                }
            ]
